properties.name: hs_last_email_activity
properties.label: Last email activity
properties.description: The type of the last email activity with the contact associated with the ticket.
properties.calculationFormula:
if (not (is_present(createdate)) or not (is_present(string(hs_last_email_details)))) then 'ORIGINAL_FROM_CONTACT'
elseif (is_present(hs_originating_email_engagement_id) and contains(string(hs_last_email_details), concatenate('[', string(hs_originating_email_engagement_id), ':'))) then 'ORIGINAL_FROM_CONTACT'
elseif contains(string(hs_last_email_details), ':EMAIL]') then 'SENT_TO_CONTACT' else 'REPLY_FROM_CONTACT'
